videos.description: Rutgers QB Giovanni Rescigno tosses a long pass to WR Andre Patton, who is left wide open for a 68-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Rutgers WR Andre Patton left wide open for TD

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Rutgers WR Andre Patton left wide open for TD) 2016/11/05 ESHEET

videos.description: Indiana QB Richard Lagow tosses a pass to WR Ricky Jones, who bounces off a tackle and goes 36 yards for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Indiana WR Ricky Jones breaks a tackle for TD

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Indiana WR Ricky Jones breaks a tackle for TD) 2016/11/05 ESHEET

videos.description: Indiana QB Zander Diamont fumbles the ball and Rutgers DL Darnell Davis scoops it up and returns it 75 yards for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Rutgers' Darnell Davis returns fumble for TD
